来。人会自动获得合法身份，动物如果是恐龙之类的话，你自己想办法藏好吧。 好了，就是这些条件，大家开始头脑风暴吧。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7715c8662875b8f3b3303dbe0fdfb917_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/12979690166"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI+LbuoPOr+YkYEAMaCTExMzU3MTQ2OSDG++O9BjAAOFhAHHILMTI5Nzk2OTAxNjZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1741710639.695502", "card_id": "Q_14113441887", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 49}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孙刘联盟破裂到底怪谁？孙权偷袭荆州该不该背锅？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "说是盟友，结果孙权背后捅刀抢地盘。你说他阴险，还是刘备先赖着荆州不还活该？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-43d9cfe1d88a37f4513ad1a4e17bbc7c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/14113441887"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI+LbuoPOr+YkYEAMaCTExMzc5ODE4MyDVi5++BjAAOERAHXILMTQxMTM0NDE4ODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}], "paging": {"is_end": true, "is_start": false, "next": "", "previous": "", "totals": 0}, "fresh_text": "热榜已更新", "display_num": 15, "display_first": true, "fb_bill_main_rise": 0, "head_zone": {"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1857515993426948096", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NnITMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NngA", "tag": "辟谣", "tag_bg_color": "GRD01A"}]}, "head_zones": [{"type": "billboard_lantern", "data": [{"id": "1857515993426948096", "link_url": "https://www.zhihu.com/appview/community_construction", "title": "辟谣专区", "source_type": 0, "attached_info": "Ci4QABoTMTg1NzUxNTk5MzQyNjk0ODA5NnITMTg1N